"information on applying a texture to a mesh's material.Special "
"considerations for Bump and Normal Maps is:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/textures/properties/influence/bump_and_normal.rst:75
msgid "When using a Bump map, map the texture to *Normal* and enable *No RGB*."
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/textures/properties/influence/bump_and_normal.rst:76
msgid "When using a Normal map, map the texture to *Normal*."
msgstr ""

